{"tid":356580,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[求推介]尋找深水埗美食","createTime":"2017-08-12T07:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T03:50:05.000Z","uid":31521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e501ce679a9a9a7bff80522f29de64e9a65b751","tid":356580,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"成日要去深水埗黃金附近返工<br />\n但食嚟食去都係嗰啲<br />\n求各位食神推介深水埗美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n文記 長期被吹捧 開多咗分店都係長期好多人排 普通車仔麵 對比幾年前食仲細碗咗<br />\n劉森記 蝦籽撈正 但唔平<br />\n維記 我個人幾好豬膶 但麻麻地佢個豬膶麵 仲要長期咁多人 不了<br />\n川味 性價比高 平平地大大碗 但味道一般<br />\n泰潮 味道唔差 但貴 唔多抵食<br />\n雲南小鍋米線 算平但好淡味<br />\n隱家 西九沾麵 水準不俗"},{"pid":"fb23b750ce65fcaff3eb85418facf913dca1e32d","tid":356580,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"街邊檔車仔麵》文記"},{"pid":"69225bbbeda9b572dce1a80d9a761fd76842d7f6","tid":356580,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家食J"},{"pid":"8491cbe0a8467686c8682130355beaa8e97b38d0","tid":356580,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f2517334765cb84889730d6f86334305d1d4404","tid":356580,"uid":81141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街邊檔車仔麵》文記</blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔明點解街邊檔好食過文記<br />\n但文記永遠都排長龍<br />\n（唔通真係為左文記支花枝油？）<br />\n個人覺得文記勁鹹"},{"pid":"71fe2d689fc69950182a100da5b2785d0fbed395","tid":356580,"uid":26385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"圓方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c683b72d674fc0dea26e3a5845a9afe3dad893","tid":356580,"uid":81141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"米線 ：麻辣川隻溏心蛋正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.g